.SH NAME
\*LXmTextFieldSetErrorSelection \*O\(em A TextField function that sets the primary selection of the text
.iX "XmTextFieldSetErrorSelection"
.iX "TextField functions" "XmTextFieldSetErrorSelection"
.SH SYNOPSIS
.sS
.iS
\&#include <Xm/TextF.h>
.sp \n(PDu
void XmTextFieldSetErrorSelection (\*Vwidget, first, last, time\*L)
.ta .5i 1.7i
	Widget	\*Vwidget\*L;
	XmTextPosition	\*Vfirst\*L;
	XmTextPosition	\*Vlast\*L;
	Time	\*Vtime\*L;
.wH .fi
.ne 10
.iE
.sE
.SH DESCRIPTION
\*LXmTextFieldSetErrorSelection\*O sets the primary selection of the text in the
widget using the SgNerrorBackground color to draw the selected text 
backgroung color.
It also sets the insertion cursor position to the last position of the
selection and calls the widget's \*LXmNmotionVerifyCallback\*O callbacks.
.VL .75i 
.LI "\*Vwidget\*O"
Specifies the Text widget ID
.LI "\*Vfirst\*O"
Marks the first character position of the text to be selected
.LI "\*Vlast\*O"
Marks the last position of the text to be selected
.LI "\*Vtime\*O"
Specifies the time at which the selection value is desired.  This should
be the same as the time of the event that triggered this request.
.LE 
.PP 
